description: Table showing a) the number and percentage of Jobseekers Allowance (JSA) terminations who flow on to Income Support (IS), b) the number and percentage of Jobseekers Allowance (JSA) terminations who flow on to Incapacity Benefit (IB) or Severe Disablement Allowance (SDA) and c) the number and percentage of Jobseekers Allowance (JSA) terminations who flow back on to JSA; for all ages in Great Britain. 10 p.
